<br>
Perhaps nonsensical, sincce we have no idea of anybody in any position of power is actually considering it, but it still has merit, since it is a strong possibility that it could someday happen, and maybe we're coming up with some ways it could become feasible.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&gt; seems to me it would be a better design with a directional<br>
blast. Indiscriminate detonations would be wasting half of their<br>
energy when the blast wave facing away from the spacecraft<br>
